{
  "stem": "15694.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And look, but didn't touch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But one day, I found that the top of the butter and the top of the cheese had like a design on-- on them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was wondering.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, ah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somebody wants to find out if it had been touched.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was too-- too much of a challenge-- challenge for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I got myself a knife, lifted the butter, and cut about a millimeter off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had no bread at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Should I give it to Mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Share it with sister.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What will they say?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it-- it wasn't done, such a thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So who can remember the taste of butter after so many years?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, I did-- I can.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And later on, I sort of found that, you know, I-- I change it, sometimes to-- same way, bit of cheese.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes a bit of butter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't have a bad conscience because every time something was finished, it was immediately renewed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't suffer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was still in prison.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the most peculiar thing of all which happened, you know, in-- in all these years, I cannot remember the moment, which must have been a very big moment, when Father joined us again.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I remember him being with us, and with his ingenuity we had to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during the time-- oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- we sold-- before he-- before he came out, we sold the first thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what my mother decided, of course, was my-- an old winter coat, my father's winter coat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had the-- the food which we brought-- brought to my father daily had of stopped, and he must have realized we had-- we were on bad times.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
